@page "/"
@attribute [StreamRendering]

<PageTitle>Home</PageTitle>

<div class="flex-col" style="padding: 0.5rem">
    <h1>Hello, world!</h1>
    <div class="flex">
        <Button Text="Primary Button" OnClick="() => showAlert = true" />
        <Button Text="Destructive Button" Type="ButtonType.Destructive" />
    </div>

    <Calendar Date="date" DateChanged="d => date = d" />
    <p>Because there is no interactivity, components will only render in their initial state and stay non-interactive.<br />However, if you chose to make a page interactive either Server of WebAssembly or even Auto, they will start working.</p>

    @if (showAlert)
    {
        <Alert Title="Sysinfocus simple/ui" Description="Congratulations! you have successfully installed Sysinfocus simple/ui components." />
        <Separator />
        <AboutSysinfocus />
    }
</div>

@code
{
    bool showAlert;
    DateTime? date;
}